snippet.title: How Mera’s Aquaman Look Could Signal Change to the DCEU! (Nerdist News w/ Jessica Chobot)
snippet.description:
While Justice League hasn’t even hit theaters, we’re already getting a look at the Aquaman solo flick thanks to a pic of Amber Heard’s Mera, but this could be much more than just a sneak peek! Jessica takes a deeper dive on today's Nerdist News!

Would you welcome the change in tone? Let us know in the comments below!
